Package: poxchat-plugin-checksum
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Depends:
 poxchat (= ${binary:Version}),
 ${shlibs:Depends},
 ${misc:Depends},
Description: DCC file checksum plugin for PoxChat
 PoxChat is a GTK4 IRC client, forked from HexChat.
 .
 This plugin computes and verifies SHA-256 checksums for DCC file
 transfers, allowing the recipient to confirm that the file arrived
 intact.

Package: poxchat-plugin-fishlim
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Depends:
 poxchat (= ${binary:Version}),
 ${shlibs:Depends},
 ${misc:Depends},
Description: FiSH end-to-end channel encryption plugin for PoxChat
 PoxChat is a GTK4 IRC client, forked from HexChat.
 .
 This plugin implements the FiSH encryption protocol (Blowfish in
 ECB/CBC modes with DH1080 key exchange), allowing encrypted private
 messages and channel conversations with other FiSH-capable clients.

Package: poxchat-plugin-sysinfo
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Depends:
 poxchat (= ${binary:Version}),
 pciutils,
 ${shlibs:Depends},
 ${misc:Depends},
Description: System information plugin for PoxChat
 PoxChat is a GTK4 IRC client, forked from HexChat.
 .
 This plugin adds a /sysinfo command that posts a summary of the
 host system (CPU, RAM, OS, graphics adapter) to the active channel.
